cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CY 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and summarization. It may also belong to cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as the paper discusses strategies for organizing information from multiple documents. Additionally, the paper may fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it proposes a methodology for studying the properties of ordering information and implements a strategy for ordering information. Finally, cs.CY (Computers and Society) is a possibility as the paper discusses the problem of organizing information in the news genre.
